    "description": "DHL India Digital Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Supply Chain Manager for our Jodhpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout DHL India Digital Technologies:\nDHL India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DHL India Digital Technologies!",
